  "raw_content": "Decoder性能分析\nQKV-Linear\n\n\nshape=(B,M,K,N)\n\n(1, 16, 4096, 4096)\n\n(1, 16, 8192, 2560)\n\n(1, 32, 4096, 4096)\n\n(1, 32, 8192, 2560)\n\nperSpc\n\n(1, 16, 4096, 256)\n\n(1, 16, 8192, 160)\n\n(1, 32, 4096, 256)\n\n(1, 16, 8192, 160)\n\nload_a_hbm_to_gib\n\n64 x 4096 x 2 / 60 = 8,738\n\n64 x 8192 x 2 / 60 = 17,476\n\n64 x 4096 x 2 / 60 = 8,738\n\n64 x 8192 x 2 / 60 = 17,476\n\nload_b_hbm_to_gib\n\n4096 x 256 x 1 / 40 = 26214\n\n8192 x 256 x 1 / 40 = 52,428\n\n4096 x 256 x 1 / 40 = 26214\n\n8192 x 256 x 1 / 40 = 52,428\n\ngemm\n\n64 x 4096 x 256 / 16384 = 8192\n\n64 x 8192 x 256 / 16384 = 8192\n\n64 x 4096 x 256 / 16384 = 8192\n\n64 x 8192 x 256 / 16384 = 8192\n\nL2_add\n\n64 x 256 x (4096 / 2048) x 4 / 256 = 512\n\n64 x 256 x (8192 / 2048) x 4 / 256 = 1,024\n\n64 x 256 x (4096 / 2048) x 4 / 256 = 512\n\n64 x 256 x (8192 / 2048) x 4 / 256 = 1,024\n\ntypecast\n\n64 x 256 x 2 / 30 = 1092\n\n64 x 256 x 2 / 30 = 1,092\n\n64 x 256 x 2 / 30 = 1092\n\n64 x 256 x 2 / 30 = 1,092\n\nres\n\nmax( load_a_hbm_to_gib + load_b， gemm, l2_add)\n+ typecast\n= 27380\n\n70,996\n\n27380\n\n70,996\n",
